				<td colspan="2"><span>As of last night i had been using a Ornate Stone Battlehammer and Trueborns Dagger of Rites or whatever name is.  Last night i bought the Soulpeircer 15/19 dagger that procs rune 1. So now im duelwielding 2 daggers. There would be nothing wrong with this is there? My 1HS is 206 atm and my 1HBlunt and Piercing is maxed... Is there another weapon that is tradeable for a bard that i can buy. IMO i really dont think so. Ive been in bazaar every night doing searchs and atm i cant find anything else to duel wield that would put out more dps... I also look for HP, ill sacrifice a dmg point etc for more hp/mana. Both my weapons are 80 HP/Mana/End... I think these are the best atm. Any suggestions... I take that back, the sword that drops in MPG in tactics is better but i cant afford 150k atm and i know the trident from RS is excellent but i think thats no drop...</span></td>
