				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Duelwielding Daggers?<a name="72778"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 31 05 4:12 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I'm not sure if a <a target="_new" href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=17179&quot; target=&quot;_blank">Polished Obsidian Tomahawk</a> is what you're looking for, but it is a useful alternative.  While it doesn't have as much stats, you do prevent losing more hp every time the rune procs.  It has adds a 200 hp rune, 40 str, and -20 agi.  It helps to take some of the bite out of getting smacked during pulls.  Unfortunately, the str component causes the proc not to stack with a few shammy buffs, but overall, I've found it to be pretty useful.</span></td>
